<div class="related_info">
  






  

  <h2>
    <span>内容简介</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>



<div class="indent" id="link-report">
    
      <div class="">
        <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>《古文观止》是清康熙年间吴乘权、吴大职编选的一部古文读本，凡十二卷，收录自先秦至明末的散文二百二十二篇，每篇都有注释和评论。据《左传》襄公二十九年记载，吴公子季札在鲁国观看乐舞《韶�》时，以为尽善尽美，无以复加，赞叹道：“观止矣：若有他乐吾不敢请已！”本书书名中“观止”二字即由此而来，是表示所选的古文极好，堪称最佳读本。</p></div>

      </div>
    

</div>

  
      

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img9.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/other/online-partner.36905.css">

  <div class="online-partner">

    <div class="online-type">
      <span>在线试听：</span>
        <div class="online-read-or-audio">
          <a class="impression_track_mod_buyinfo" target="_blank" href="https://www.ximalaya.com/growth/v3/album/59139057?ch=49&amp;tab=2&amp;utm_source=douban" data-track="https://frodo.douban.com/rohirrim/tracking/impression?subject_id=1014561&amp;isbn=7101000290&amp;source=ximalaya&amp;user_id=&amp;bid=oDT-H0qlJns&amp;platform=pc&amp;location=vender_subject_text" onclick="track('https://frodo.douban.com/rohirrim/tracking/click?subject_id=1014561&amp;isbn=7101000290&amp;source=ximalaya&amp;user_id=&amp;bid=oDT-H0qlJns&amp;platform=pc&amp;location=vender_subject_text')">
            <img width="16" height="16" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/rohirrim/6bd2847c065ab16da2b96d1660ea25c4ea017cb9/website/static/pics/icon/icon_ximalaya.png" />
            <span>喜马拉雅</span>
          </a>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  




<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/subject/authors_section.6022b.css">

<h2>
    
  

  <h2>
    <span>古文观止的创作者</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


</h2>
<div class="indent">
    <p></p>
    <div id="authors" class="authors">
    <ul class="authors-list from-subject __oneline">
            
            <li class="author">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4504805/" title="吴楚材">
                    <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/pics/author-default-medium.png" alt="吴楚材" class="avatar">
                </a>
                <div class="info">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4504805/" title="吴楚材" class="name">吴楚材</a>
                    <span class="role">作者</span>
                </div>
            </li>
             
        <li class="author fake fake5"></li>
    </ul>
    </div>
</div>

  




  


  


  


  


    
  

  <h2>
    <span>作者简介</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>



      <div class="indent ">
          
            <div class="">
            <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>吴乘权和吴大职是叔侄二人，浙江山阴（今绍兴）人。吴乘权字楚村，博览经史，学识丰富，一生以授馆为业，所著除《古文观止》外，尚有《纲鉴易知录》传世。吴大职字调侯，秉承家学，颇有才气。他同叔父吴乘权一起在家乡“课业子弟”。《古文观止》就是他们教授弟子诵读古文的讲义。</p></div>

            </div>
      </div>

  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  


  





  

  
    




  

